deleted file mode 100644
index 785e538..0000000
--- a/commit_msg.txt
+++ /dev/null
@@ -1,31 +0,0 @@
-feat: server-side chat group idempotency, real behavioural tests, helper extraction
-
-Backend: add chat_group_idempotency_keys table with unique constraint on
-(creator_id, idempotency_key). POST /chat/groups now reads X-Idempotency-Key,
-computes payload hash, checks for existing response inside transaction, returns
-cached response on retry, rejects key reuse with different payload (409 conflict).
-ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING handles concurrent identical requests safely.
-
-Migration 046_chat_group_idempotency.sql creates the table and index.
-
-Backend tests: 10 new tests in chatGroupIdempotency.test.ts covering payload
-hashing, first request (miss), sequential retry (hit), same key/different payload
-(conflict), concurrent retry safety, cross-user key independence.
-
-Frontend: extracted pure helpers from production code for real testing:
-- chatGroupHelpers.ts: member filtering, validation, toggle, search query checks
-- messageGrouping.ts: cluster first/last detection, system message, day change
-- messageContextMenuCapabilities.ts: action derivation from capabilities
-
-CreateGroupChatScreen, ChatScreen, MessageContextMenu now import and use these
-extracted helpers instead of inline logic.
-
-Removed synthetic chatGroupVisualCompletion.test.ts (60 tests asserting
-locally created constants and static source strings).
-
-Added chatRuntimeBehaviour.test.ts: 49 real behavioural tests importing and
-exercising production helper functions, mocking searchUsers, testing idempotency
-key lifecycle, duplicate submit blocking, search error/retry, message grouping,
-and context menu capability derivation.
-
-No device available for visual sign-off (adb not found on system).
